{"id":21070,"title":"[Infection prevention is everyone's responsibility].","abstract":"All healthcare players, wherever they practise, are concerned by infection prevention. To help them, hospital hygiene teams communicate national policies, spread prevention messages, provide information and work tirelessly to raise awareness. The aim is to promote the hygiene reflex with every procedure which brings the caregiver into contact with the patient.","date":"2014-03-14","categories":"Bacterial Infections and Mycoses","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24624719","annotations":[{"name":"Health care","weight":0.801318,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_care"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.676072,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Infection","weight":0.567881,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infection"},{"name":"Communication","weight":0.544842,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Communication"},{"name":"Preventive medicine","weight":0.461886,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Preventive_medicine"},{"name":"Information","weight":0.404527,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Information"},{"name":"Hospital","weight":0.346584,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hospital"},{"name":"Awareness","weight":0.16053,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Awareness"},{"name":"Hygiene","weight":0.149429,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hygiene"},{"name":"Caregiver","weight":0.0478909,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caregiver"},{"name":"Reflex","weight":0.0377168,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reflex"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.029746,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Infection control","weight":0.0223718,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Infection_control"}]}
